      "extra": {
        "message": "Missing Rate Limiting on Login Endpoint\n\nThe /login endpoint has no rate limiting mechanism. An attacker can make unlimited login attempts to brute-force credentials.\n\nImpact: An attacker can perform unlimited brute-force attacks against user accounts to guess passwords.\n\nFix: Implement rate limiting on the login endpoint using a library like Flask-Limiter.",
