      "extra": {
        "message": "Pickle Import \u2014 Potential Insecure Deserialization\n\nThe pickle module and base64 decoding functions are imported, suggesting potential pickle deserialization functionality. While no explicit pickle.loads() call is visible in this file, the imports of pickle, b64decode, and b64encode together indicate infrastructure for insecure deserialization that may be used in other parts of the application or planned for future use.\n\nImpact: If pickle deserialization is used with user-controlled input elsewhere, it enables arbitrary code execution. The presence of these imports alongside base64 functions is a strong indicator of a deserialization endpoint.\n\nFix: Remove unused pickle imports. If serialization is needed, use safe formats like JSON. Never deserialize untrusted data with pickle.",
